== History ==
[[File:Jingu-shinden 01.JPG|thumb|right|256px|The sacred rice fields (Shinden) of {{ill|Ise Grand Shrine|ja|伊勢神宮|12=draft}}
[[File:Jingu-sinden-otaue 03.jpg|thumb|right|256px|Rice planting ceremony in the sacred fields of the shrine]]
[[File:Yushima-Tenmagu-01.jpg|thumb|right|256px|Sacred rice harvest ceremony at {{ill|Yushima Tenman-gū|ja|湯島天満宮|12=draft}}
